Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.69,0:00:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉那就在那里面…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个荒凉的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没什么研究内容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.26,0:00:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 普莉姆拉正等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们果然来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来见普莉姆拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是说不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.73,0:00:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时与神和恶魔为敌  你该不是想强行突破吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.46,0:01:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让凛大人和莉姆见一面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.47,0:01:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神王大人 魔王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.24,0:01:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让凛和莉姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.91,0:01:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.22,0:01:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是凛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选他做希亚的女婿还真做对了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.51,0:01:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么做就怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是两个傻瓜老爸而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.69,0:01:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且对女人的请求耳根子软吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.73,0:01:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要谢的话去谢小姑娘们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆在等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.27,0:02:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
