Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,↑Title↑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常森严呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.23,0:02:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然墙壁看上去只是普通的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却砌入了强力的防御魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过上次就把研究所给炸飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是发生那种事情就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说奇怪的话 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这不是玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.71,0:02:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为有此危险 我才不希望你们来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 也不能丢下普莉姆拉不管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有小凛的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我想说真不愧是希亚的女婿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做个约定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:03:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果途中普莉姆拉的情况恶化的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候让我们立刻使用最终手段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 那就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是把普莉姆拉的感情清除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 如果这一条你不遵守话就头痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛先生 你不想把她们都卷进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和凛在一起不管遇到什么事都没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你约定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔话说的有理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们之间的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:03:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等您很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉
