Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快好起来 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 回去吧
