Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.49,0:06:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去就会和1号实验体一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么只有清除…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛先生 别起来 趴下
