Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在普莉姆拉从溶液里出来性命就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 对不起了 凛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不等再等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:08:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莉奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来吧 普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔力控制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莉奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉可莉斯…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉可莉斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后还能见一面 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小琳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔力基本安定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么莉姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概不会再失控了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:11:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为拥有感情就能控制魔力的假说并没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是会因为其变化引起一时的魔力失控吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.38,0:11:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那也可能就轰地一下炸咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 恐怕能顺利度过这种失控的可能性连1%都不满
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇迹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那孩子救了两次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们就得到了完全体了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后对普莉姆拉进行研究的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这尤古多拉西鲁计划也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把普莉姆拉带回家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 这是神界和魔界投入全力的顶尖计划
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意见能有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输了 输了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让普莉姆拉回人界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是偶然的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道什么时候再失控
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 那时候小凛不在的话也制止不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人界生活 再增加更丰富的感情的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉也就更能控制魔力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前交给凛先生比较安全
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样了 小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜啊 恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 爸爸你适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上就让我们喝个痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 小凛也来一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 不喝我们敬的酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 喝太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追加下酒菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看星星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪颗是莉可莉斯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉可莉斯姐姐的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这次即没好好道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有好好道别
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她救了 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…却对她没一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉可莉斯姐姐一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莉奈 希亚 枫 大家真的帮了我不少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:14:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这发带 一直鼓舞我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚沙前辈  谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是借你发带
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那时候我感觉到有人在对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作起来 快振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像亚沙前辈一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到害怕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到很可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一想起亚沙前辈在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算捧我也不会奖励你什么你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别拍我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过前辈好像精神了不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然还没有恢复到平常状态
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周大概就能去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试下治疗魔法怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.37,0:14:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对魔法有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.23,0:14:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那样做也行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡一觉就治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:15:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这样说 但不快点好起来 我会头痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么凛会头痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 想对姐姐隐瞒什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚沙前辈 不在的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直被前辈帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是这次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我困扰的时候 总是因亚沙前辈的只言片语
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而开始改变
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不能很好表达
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈在我身边真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 我是小凛的救助专员咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我这个可靠的姐姐就好好照顾你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 有个不听话坏弟弟还真辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意 我是个坏弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚沙前辈  没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去打水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不舒服的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛说了奇怪的话我笑过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时雨前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很喜欢凛大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚沙前辈 看上去也很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就又解决了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 也不是皆大欢喜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有她…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:16:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.77,0:17:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便说点话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这公园您还记得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔了8年后再次和奈莉奈见面…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我和凛大人初次见面的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 8年前也是在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 前一阵子是我第一次到人界来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这公园第一次遇到您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8年前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到凛大人的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8年前的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替生病而无法行动的我来到人界的莉可莉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来后很高兴地说起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一个男孩子度过的如同宝物般的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的最初的也是最后的 得到的唯一的真正的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 他叫凛 非常温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 奈莉奈的名字里也有凛的发音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么之后就把奈莉奈叫做琳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就算无法见面也不会寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去见面的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉可…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果有一天琳去了人界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要去见他哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替我 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 莉可莉斯把生命给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我剩下的生命力给她的话 一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 莉可莉斯是奈莉奈大人的克隆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这生命力注入的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 那么你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能救重要的人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我体内有她的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的生命力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那美妙的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连那份思念也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对那位名为土见凛的男孩的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为莉可莉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为莉可莉斯实现她的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是为了实现莉可莉斯的思念才来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…作为奈莉奈的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却有了和莉可莉斯一样的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和凛大人度过的时光是那么愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因为体内有莉可莉斯才喜欢你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是身为奈莉奈喜欢上你了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真笨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想成为莉可莉斯的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在那魔界研究所里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉可莉斯的思念终于实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉可莉斯一直都很想说那句话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么她一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到了一直最喜欢的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 留下的是我的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉可莉斯消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:20:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是喜欢凛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.26,0:21:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份回忆是只属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从此对凛大人的思念只是奈莉奈的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以更喜欢凛大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许凛大人心里还有别的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那种人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一样 对自己的感情还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然喜欢凛大人的心情是不会变的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但让我心中的爱意扩大 好像还需要点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不输给任何人之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 当我能以自己的歌声歌唱时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您能听听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.57,0:22:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 这是在此之前的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.35,0:23:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于回到往常的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.71,0:23:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 确实是有什么东西在逐渐地变化
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.79,0:23:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.14,0:23:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没精神哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.12,0:24:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 SHUFFLE第16话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.32,0:24:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桔梗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.26,0:24:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只让我一个人享受这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.35,0:24:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是不行吧
